<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="section-tag">Our Story</p>
        <h2>A Family Business with Deep Agricultural Roots</h2>
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>Eric and Julie Hamilton own and operate Midwest Grain Roasters. Both come from rural Western Illinois — Julie grew up on a small farm, and Eric worked on his dad's farm and family ag service business.</p>
          <p>The Hamilton family has been in agricultural services for generations. Eric's father and grandfather ran Hamilton Soil Service, a fertilizer and ag chemical company that expanded across Western Illinois. This included Midwest Fertilizer Exchange, a liquid blending business, and a Kent feed dealership transformed into Illini Feeds.</p>
          <p>During his time in the family business, Don Hamilton purchased the first grain Roast-A-Matic roaster. Originally intended as a stationary process, he was convinced by Dale Schnupp of Roast-A-Matic to go portable. After a trip or two to Wisconsin, the decision was made to start Midwest Grain Roasters.</p>
          <p>In the spring of 1991, Eric and Julie moved to Spring Green, Wisconsin. They've been serving agriculture ever since.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-quote">
          <blockquote>
            "Our sincere thank you goes out to all our customers we've worked for through the years."
          </blockquote>
          <cite>— Eric & Julie Hamilton</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-side">
        <div class="about-fact-card">
          <div class="fact-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="28" height="28"><path d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Founded in 1989</h4>
          <p>Over three decades of on-site grain roasting experience</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-fact-card">
          <div class="fact-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="28" height="28"><path d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Dodgeville, Wisconsin</h4>
          <p>Serving farmers and feed mills across the Midwest</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-fact-card">
          <div class="fact-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="28" height="28"><path d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.249-8.25-3.286z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Fully Insured</h4>
          <p>Midwest Grain Roasters, Inc. is a fully insured corporation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-fact-card">
          <div class="fact-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="28" height="28"><path d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Year-Round Service</h4>
          <p>We roast for our customers all year, not just during harvest</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 7rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-earth);
    color: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-wheat-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-quote {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-wheat-dark);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-wheat);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  cite {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .about-side {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-fact-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .fact-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-wheat-dark);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .about-fact-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .about-fact-card p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
